      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE OZZY (6) has a superb record at this track and trip, unbeaten so far from three starts. Comes off a (24.52) win last time, scoring by 4.5 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 440m at this track. Looks a key chance on best form. DAZZLE YOU (7) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. In the money last time at this track (24.82) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4.5 lengths second. Looks one of the chances. JAYLA MAGIC (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (25.04) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Can find the frame this time. CANYA PONGA (3) has claims again if he runs up to the latest effort.",
